Cell["\<\
Strangely enough the digits after the initial 0. count up from 0 to 8 then \
back down to 0, and stay there. What about a different number of 1s?\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.984858495231745*^9, 
  3.984858586428005*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"76c2520c-8376-9645-a162-\
