Cell["\<\
So the digits increase from 0 to 8, stay at 8 for another 4 counts, then \
decrease down to 0.   Can the diagonal picture explain that?\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.98485923141733*^9, 3.9848592749894276`*^9}, {
  3.9849311520288105`*^9, 3.984931155902302*^9}, {3.984934742525587*^9, 
