Cell["\<\
Now the \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]hold\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] at the top is \
only 1, the difference between 8 & 9. How to think of this? The increase \
continued up to column \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]8\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], the \
hold until column \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]9\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], and after \
that, the descent.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9848592813943977`*^9, 
