Cell["\<\
Now we count up from 00 to 08, hold the 08 until column 15 (7 additional \
columns), then count back down to 00. No carries to worry about.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9849299821458015`*^9, 3.984930035463852*^9}, {
  3.9850274035541096`*^9, 3.9850274241353817`*^9}, {3.985027459910227*^9, 
